{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/extras/920x430_HeaderCapsule.png?t=1730426824\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kristala is a dark fantasy ARPG featuring Sekiro-inspired combat, acrobatic parkour, and exploration to uncover a detailed story. Celebrate Kristaloween with our spooky, collector's helms, available to all players for a limited time in honor of Kristala's Chapter II release.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/extras/600x22-main-center-divider.png?t=1730426824\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> The Hallowed Lantern Helm</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On All Hallows' Eve, per Myr\u2019s annual crypt-cleansing, Nisargans gather \u2018round to whittle gourds and various root vegetables to frighten off wayward souls wandered from the Hallowed Haunts. A curious tradition adopted by all Anagativan clans.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>A pumpkin carved in the likeness of a blazing ghoul\u2014nicked by pranksters, no doubt.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/extras/helm-jacko.gif?t=1730426824\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/extras/600x22-main-center-divider.png?t=1730426824\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Pyromaster Skull Helm\u00a0</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>\u201c\u2018Tis better to burn the brightest than to fade a flame\u201d, a Keozan proverb some pyromancers take all too literally.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>The ever-burning skull of Pyromaster Romy, sifted from her ashes.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/extras/helm-skull.gif?t=1730426824\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/extras/600x22-main-center-divider.png?t=1730426824\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Both the Pyromaster Skull and Flaming Lantern helms are available to all players who already have Kristala in their library, and available to new players for a limited time following our Chapter II release.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/extras/helm-pump-skull-1.png?t=1730426824\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/extras/helm-pump-skull-2.png?t=1730426824\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730426824","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/page.bg.jpg?t=1730426824","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/7177b3191b100b2aaf9c6d813427dd60c199e949/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730426824","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/7177b3191b100b2aaf9c6d813427dd60c199e949/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1730426824","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Downloadable Content","id":21},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274920/extras/920x430_HeaderCapsule.png?t=1730426824\" /></p><p class=\"bb_pa